_sText:
v2 Changelog:
file size cut down hugely (61 zip to a 20 zip)
songs cut down (1 removed)
custom textures made smaller (file size)
added decals
football now in VIP
pool made slightly larger
various other tweaks and fixes

This v2 is a beta release currently - it is made upon the tested v1 and has been tweaked, there should be little to no problems. Please do report any.

Feel free to add on steam: mrburns4


***32 Players***
***22 T Spawn points***
***10 CT Spawn points***

***I permit anyone to use any part of this map, provided I remain credited AND the texture stating what area it is remains intact in whole***

Features: Mr Wolf, Bulldogs, Musical Chairs, Red light Green light, olympics(shotput, long jump, bhop, race, race of death) skate, nade war, war zone, dark room, maze, disco, pool, trivia zone, obstacle course, game zone

v3 changes (coming soon) : retexture, 3d skybox, removal of some help buttons, addition of some new games
